WEBVTT

00:12:58.608 --> 00:13:00.517
was not just an act of humanity,

00:13:00.517 --> 00:13:03.419
it was making a real difference
for the people.

00:13:03.419 --> 00:13:06.670
Why could he not understand this?

00:13:06.670 --> 00:13:08.597
We have a responsibility to try.

00:13:08.597 --> 00:13:12.431
You've heard about that concept:
Responsibility to Protect.

00:13:12.431 --> 00:13:16.512
Outcomes may depend
on various parameters.

00:13:16.512 --> 00:13:20.369
We may even fail,
but there is worse than failing --

00:13:20.369 --> 00:13:23.120
it's not even trying when we can.

00:13:24.441 --> 00:13:28.316
Well, if you are met this way,
if you sign up for this sort of job,

00:13:28.316 --> 00:13:32.954
your life is going to be full
of joy and sadness,